description: Defines DTO classes for profile update requests and profile responses in the FrndAppBackend project.

classes.name: UpdateProfileRequest
classes.description: Request DTO for updating the current user's profile, including optional DisplayName and Bio fields with maximum length constraints.

classes.name: ProfileResponse
classes.description: Response DTO representing user's profile data, including Id, Email, UserName, optional DisplayName and Bio, and CreatedAt timestamp.
